RESTING IN GODS ✝️ 
PRESENCE 💨 IS NOT NECESSARILY IDLENESS.

When we relax in HIS ✝️ Presence 💨, it demonstrates trust in HIM✝️ .

Trust 👍🏻 is a rich 💰 word, laden with meaning and direction for ones  life 🧬.
GOD ✝️ wants us to lean on, trust 👍🏻, and be confident in HIM ✝️.

When we lean on HIM ✝️ for support, GOD ✝️ delights 👏 in our trusting 👍🏻 confidence.

We must trust 👍🏻 HIM ✝️ 
not only for the salvation 
🙌🏼 of our souls (💰&🧠 )  but also for the direction of our lives 🧬.
It must be a commitment without reserve,—{ spirit 🌬, soul ❤️&🧠, and body.

Many people 👨🏻‍🤝‍👨🏿 turn away when they get exhausted 😩.  Associating GOD ✝️ with duty 👷🏼 and diligence😓, and try hiding from HIS PRESENCE 💨when they need a break from work.  This saddens GOD!

There must be a ‘healthy’ 🙏🏽 distrust 👎🏼 of self, an acknowledge 💭 that we do not know 🤔 what is best for us, that we 🤔   are not capable of guiding   🦮👩🏼‍🦯 ourselves.

Jeremiah expressed it pointedly . “O LORD ✝️,
I know the way of man 👨 is not in himself; it is not in man 👨 who walks to direct his own steps 👣.”
      ( Jeremiah 10:23 )

GOD ✝️ spoke through the prophet Isaiah:
For thus said the LORD GOD ✝️ , the Holy One ☝️ of Israel 🇮🇱: In returning ↩️ [ to ME✝️ ] and resting 😴 [ in ME ✝️ ] you shall be saved 😇; in quietness and in [ trusting ] 👍🏻 confidence shall be your strength 💪🏼. —But you would not.
     ( Isaiah 30:15 )

Lean 😍 on , trust 👍🏻 in, and be confident 😎 in the LORD ✝️ with all your heart ❤️ and mind 🧠 and do not rely on your own insight 👁 or understanding 🤔💭.
